export const advancedQuestionsTwo = [
  {
    id: 0,
    questionNumber: 6,
    question: "Alfred Butts, an architect, found himself out of ____.",
    answerOptions: [
      { answerText: "earning", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "work", isCorrect: true },
      { answerText: "income", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "job", isCorrect: false },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 1,
    questionNumber: 7,
    question:
      "He decided that there was a ____ for a board game based on words",
    answerOptions: [
      { answerText: "market", isCorrect: true },
      { answerText: "purchase", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "commerce", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "sale", isCorrect: false },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 2,
    questionNumber: 8,
    question: "and ____ to design one.",
    answerOptions: [
      { answerText: "took up", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "set out", isCorrect: true },
      { answerText: "made for", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "got round", isCorrect: false },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 3,
    questionNumber: 9,
    question: "Eventually he made a ____ from it",
    answerOptions: [
      { answerText: "wealth", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "fund", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "cash", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "fortune", isCorrect: true },
    ],
  },
  {
    id: 4,
    questionNumber: 10,
    question:
      "in spite of the fact that his original ____ was only three cents a game.",
    answerOptions: [
      { answerText: "receipt", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "benefit", isCorrect: false },
      { answerText: "profit", isCorrect: true },
      { answerText: "allowance", isCorrect: false },
    ],
  },
];
